'''''TB-1''''' was one of the [[TIE/sa tactical bomber/Legends|TIE bombers]] [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] had stationed on [[Dubrillion/Legends|Dubrillion]] at the start of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. During the [[Battle of Dubrillion]], ''TB-1'' was piloted by [[Gauch]]. It was destroyed in the battle.

